reviewText:
Hosted by: Jesse The Body Ventura
Additional Commentary: Gorilla Monsoon

Lumberjack Match [Intercontinental Title]: Greg Valentine defends against Tito Santana

Indian Strap Match: Greg Valentine vs Chief Jay Strongbow

Texas Tornado Match: Jimmy Superfly Snuka & Junkyard Dog vs Rowdy Roddy Piper & Cowboy Bob Orton

All Women's Battle Royal

20-Man Battle Royal (Afa, Sika, Samu, Adrian Adonis, Dick Murdock, Iron Sheik, Paul Orndorff, Bob Orton, Rene Goulet, Ron Shaw, Tito Santana, Sgt Slaughter, Jose Luis Rivera, Butcher Vachon, Tony Garea, Chief Jay Strongbow, Steve Lombardi, Charlie Fulton, Terry Daniels, and Japanese Legend Antonio Inoki)

Steel Cage Match [Intercontinental Title]: Magnificent Muraco defends against Jimmy Superfly Snuka (features Snuka's splash from the top of the cage)

Mixed Tag Team Match With Managers: Magnificent Muraco & Captain Lou Albano vs Jimmy Superfly Snuka & Arnold Skaaland

Six-Man Tag Match: Larry Zbyszko, High Chief Peter Maivia & Haystacks Calhoun vs Moose Monroe, Butcher Vachon & Strong Kobayashi

10-Man Tag Match [3 Out Of 5 Falls]: Andre the Giant, Rocky Johnson, Salvatore Bellomo, Pedro Morales & Superfly Jimmy Snuka vs Ray The Crippler Stevens, Mr. Fuji, Magnificent Muraco, Playboy Buddy Rose & Superstar Billy Graham
